headline: Has Visa’s 73.6% Three Year Surge Already Priced In Future Growth?
summary: Wondering if Visa is still a buy at these levels, or if the easy money has already been made? Let us unpack what the current price really implies about its future. Visa has climbed 6.5% over the last month and is up 11.1% year to date, building on a strong 73.6% gain over three years. Those kinds of moves tend to signal shifting expectations around growth and risk.
